    additional_issues: Optional[str] Any additional issues found during critique


General knowledge graph facts
node_type is always one of:
Entity - Represents a person, thing or object
Event - Any short term action or occurrence, could be event of eating food or more traditional event like wedding.
State - This is really a property with temporal awareness.  State of having a job or state of having a phone number.
Goal - Aspiration with temporal awareness.
Property - Very rare, most properties should be State, only immutable properties like birthdate or place of birth are true properties
Concept - Anything that might have its own page in wikipedia.  Slightly expanded for common concepts in persons life.
You must have very good reason to change node_type.

